        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2.Nest of Auplopus cf.rufipes.(A) Arrangement of cells inside the trap nest.Scale bar = 1 cm. (B) Nest in profile showing an overlay on the first cell and the cells leaning. Scale bar = 1 cm. (C) Cell lip-shaped structure before provision.Scale bar = 0.5 cm. (D) Brood cells glued together,one of them with an emergence hole.Scale bar = 0.5cm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4983794/files/figure.png" .

